                                    </Border>
                                </StackPanel>
                            </StackPanel>
                        </Border>

                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpBody}" xml:space="preserve">Step 1: Build your pipeline in a new graph
Step 2: Save as a .mvxp project file
Step 3: In another graph, click "Import Function" in the toolbar
Step 4: Source nodes (no inputs) become function parameters
Step 5: Sink nodes (no outputs) become function return values
Step 6: Double-click the function node to view its internal structure</TextBlock>

                        <!-- ── Tutorial 7: Industrial Inspection ── -->
