Filter .............. Blur, sharpen, denoise (10)
Edge Detection ...... Canny, Sobel, Laplacian (4)
Morphology .......... Erode, dilate, open/close (3)
Threshold ........... Fixed, adaptive, Otsu (3)
Contour ............. Find, filter, analyze contours (13)
Feature Detection ... SIFT, ORB, Harris, FAST (8)
Drawing ............. Shapes, text, grid overlay (10)
Transform ........... Crop, resize, rotate, warp (8)
Histogram ........... CLAHE, equalize, backproject (4)
Arithmetic .......... Image math, bitwise ops (11)
Detection ........... Template match, Hough (9)
Segmentation ........ Watershed, GrabCut (3)
Value ............... Constants, math, compare (14)
Control ............. Loops, switch, delay (12)
Data Processing ..... CSV, string operations (7)
Communication ....... TCP, Serial port (3)
