                    <StackPanel>
                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpH1}">Technology Stack</TextBlock>

                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpH2}">Runtime</TextBlock>
                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpBody}" xml:space="preserve"><Bold>.NET 8.0</Bold> — Modern cross-platform runtime (Windows-only for WPF UI)
<Bold>C# 12</Bold> — Primary language with latest features (primary constructors, collection expressions)
<Bold>WPF</Bold> — Windows Presentation Foundation for desktop UI
<Bold>MVVM</Bold> — Model-View-ViewModel pattern via CommunityToolkit.Mvvm 8.x</TextBlock>

                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpH2}">Computer Vision</TextBlock>
                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpBody}" xml:space="preserve"><Bold>OpenCvSharp4 (4.10.x)</Bold> — .NET wrapper for OpenCV
  - Core image types: Mat, Point, Rect, Scalar, Size
  - Full OpenCV API: filters, edge detection, contours, feature detection
  - Image I/O: imread/imwrite, VideoCapture
  - Bayer pattern demosaicing for industrial cameras</TextBlock>

                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpH2}">Node Editor</TextBlock>
                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpBody}" xml:space="preserve"><Bold>Nodify 7.x</Bold> — WPF node editor library
  - NodifyEditor: main canvas with pan/zoom
  - Node, Connector: draggable node UI elements
  - PendingConnection: visual wire while dragging
  - Minimap, grid background, grouping support</TextBlock>

                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpH2}">MVVM Framework</TextBlock>
                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpBody}" xml:space="preserve"><Bold>CommunityToolkit.Mvvm 8.x</Bold>
  - [ObservableProperty] — auto-generates INotifyPropertyChanged
  - [RelayCommand] — auto-generates ICommand implementations
  - ObservableObject — base class for ViewModels
  - Source generators for boilerplate elimination</TextBlock>

                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpH2}">Serialization</TextBlock>
                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpBody}" xml:space="preserve"><Bold>System.Text.Json</Bold> — High-performance JSON serialization
  - camelCase naming policy
  - JsonElement for dynamic property deserialization
  - Supports both .mvx (plain JSON) and .mvxp (ZIP archive) formats

<Bold>System.IO.Compression</Bold> — ZIP archive support for .mvxp project files
  - Bundles graph JSON + referenced image/video assets</TextBlock>

                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpH2}">Unified Camera Node</TextBlock>
                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpBody}" xml:space="preserve"><Bold>Camera</Bold> — Single node for all camera types
  - Automatically detects USB, HIK, and Cognex cameras
  - Unified device list: select from all connected cameras
  - Properties auto-adjust based on camera type:
    USB: Width, Height, FPS, Backend (DirectShow/MSMF)
    HIK: TriggerMode, ExposureTime, Gain, Gamma, PixelFormat...
    Cognex: TriggerMode, ExposureTime, Brightness, PixelFormat

<Bold>HIKROBOT MVS SDK</Bold> — MvCameraControl.Net.dll
  - GigE Vision and USB3 Vision industrial cameras
  - Dynamic assembly loading via reflection (no compile-time dependency)

<Bold>Cognex VisionPro 9.x SDK</Bold> — Cognex.Vision.*.dll
  - GigE Vision cameras (CIC series)
  - Two-phase SDK loading: assemblies-only for enumeration, full init for acquisition</TextBlock>

                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpH2}">Execution Engine</TextBlock>
                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpBody}" xml:space="preserve"><Bold>GraphExecutor</Bold> — Custom execution engine
  - Kahn's algorithm for topological sorting
  - Dirty-flag incremental execution
  - Loop execution: For, While, ForEach with break support
  - Thread-safe graph snapshots
  - Three modes: single-shot, continuous streaming, event-driven runtime</TextBlock>

                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpH2}">Code Generation</TextBlock>
                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpBody}" xml:space="preserve"><Bold>Python Code Generator</Bold> — Converts graph to standalone Python/OpenCV script
<Bold>C# Code Generator</Bold> — Converts graph to standalone C#/OpenCvSharp code
  - Both generators follow topological order
  - Variable naming based on node names</TextBlock>

                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpH2}">ONNX Runtime</TextBlock>
                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpBody}" xml:space="preserve"><Bold>Microsoft.ML.OnnxRuntime 1.20.x</Bold>
  - MediaPipe face/hand/pose/mesh/segmentation models
  - YOLOv8 object detection models (nano~xlarge)
  - PaddleOCR detection + recognition models
  - InferenceSession with byte-loading for non-ASCII path safety
  - CPU inference (GPU optional with CUDA/DirectML provider)</TextBlock>

                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpH2}">OCR Engines</TextBlock>
                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpBody}" xml:space="preserve"><Bold>PaddleOCR (ONNX)</Bold> &#x2014; PP-OCRv5 detection + CTC recognition
  - Multilingual: Korean, Chinese, Japanese, English
  - Two-stage: text detection (DB) + text recognition (CTC decode)
  - Models: ppocr_det.onnx, ppocr_rec.onnx, ppocr_keys.txt

<Bold>Tesseract 5.2.x</Bold> &#x2014; Classic OCR engine via NuGet
  - 100+ language support with traineddata files
  - Page segmentation modes, confidence filtering
  - Word/Line/Block level detection</TextBlock>

                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpH2}">LLM/VLM Vision APIs</TextBlock>
                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpBody}" xml:space="preserve"><Bold>OpenAI GPT-4o</Bold> &#x2014; Chat Completions API with vision
<Bold>Google Gemini</Bold> &#x2014; GenerateContent API with inline_data
<Bold>Anthropic Claude</Bold> &#x2014; Messages API with base64 image
  - All use HttpClient REST API (no SDK dependency)
  - Image: Mat &#x2192; PNG &#x2192; base64 &#x2192; API
  - API keys auto-loaded from Models/API/api_config.json
  - 60-second timeout, response overlaid on output image</TextBlock>

                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpH2}">Build System</TextBlock>
                        <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource HelpBody}" xml:space="preserve"><Bold>MSBuild / dotnet CLI</Bold>
  - Multi-project solution: Core, Nodes, App
  - Core and Nodes are class libraries (UI-independent)
  - App is the WPF executable
  - NuGet package management</TextBlock>
